    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crush the<strong> cardamom pods</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife</p><p>Discard the outer green pods and add the <strong>cardamom seeds</strong> to a small bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong> and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>allspice</strong> to the bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Musakhan spice blend</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
